Package: pdmclass
Type: Package
Title: Classification of Microarray Samples using Penalized Discriminant Methods
Version: 1.28.0
Date: 2005-07-06
Author: James W. MacDonald, Debashis Ghosh, based in part on 
	pls code of Mike Denham
Maintainer: James W. MacDonald <jmacdon@med.umich.edu>
Description: This package can be used to classify microarray data using one of three
	penalized regression methods; partial least squares, principal components
	regression, or ridge regression.
License: Artistic-2.0
Depends: Biobase (>= 1.4.22), R (>= 1.9.0), fibroEset, mda
biocViews: Classification
